Omanyte (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0137: Porygon
Pokémon
#0139: Omastar →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Omanyte (TCG Pocket).

Omanyte has been featured on 15 different cards since it debuted in the Fossil expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Omanyte cards are normally Water-type or Fighting-type Stage 1 Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Omanyte

Omanyte
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
